  "summary": {
    "as": "Passed House",
    "asOf": "2023-12-12",
    "date": "2024-01-04T14:32:18Z",
    "text": "Ensuring Accountability in Agency Rulemaking Act\n\nThis bill requires, subject to a limited exception, that any agency rule promulgated under notice and comment procedures must be issued and signed by an individual who was appointed by the President and confirmed by the Senate.\n\nThe Office of Information and Regulatory Affairs must issue guidance for agencies to implement this requirement."
  },
